undice.', 'Synergism', 'Tamsulosin, Tinidazole, Ascorbic acid, Hydroflumethiazide, Chlorothiazide, Simeprevir, Lactic acid, Mitapivat, Methazolamide, Clindamycin, Trichlormethiazide, More', 'Fluorouracil, Pemetrexed, Mercaptopurine, Cladribine, Trifluridine, Floxuridine, Gemcitabine, Nelarabine, Cytarabine, Pralatrexate, Fludarabine, More', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/46191/', '[1] "Product Information. Clolar (clofarabine)." sanofi-aventis, Bridgewater, NJ.', 1767369485);
