im, Cycloserine, Ethambutol, Pyridoxine, Ethionamide, Aminosalicylic acid', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/46290/', '[1] "Product Information. Tracleer (bosentan)." Acetelion Pharmaceuticals US, Inc, South San Francisco, CA.', 1767369485);
